EXTRCASE  FORM      6
EXTROPS   FORM      6
EXTRTIME  FORM      6
.
FORM6     FORM      6
INDEX     FORM      2
.
LNO       FORM      2
.
OPTION1   FORM      2
.
PAGENO    FORM      3
PREVDATE  DIM       6
