.**********************************************************************
.*                             CLR0000                                *
.*                 Routine to Clear Local Variables                   *
.**********************************************************************
.
CLR0000   MOVE      ZERO,PAGENO
          MOVE      SP6,DOCTCLIN            * code entered
.
. ----- Clear the Clinic File Variables -----
.
          MOVE      SP6,OPCLCLIN
          PACK      OPCLDESC,SP20,SP20
